metrics_conclusion: In terms of chords and melody, The Droid Invasion is more complex than the typical song, having above average scores in Chord Complexity, Melodic Complexity, Chord-Melody Tension and Chord Progression Novelty.
key_conclusion: The Droid Invasion has sections analyzed in the following keys: C Minor,  and D Minor.  Click on the linked cheat sheets for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

metadata.editComments: In the theatrical, the second section is not raised a major second, and instead starts in C, modulating to G. This makes the Phrygian II the same chord as the VI7 (#11) in the first pass (in this case, Ab instead of Bb).
